{"tid":376833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【打風戰鬥民族】台遊客不理勸喻照外出　笑言：澳門這個is nothing!","createTime":"2017-08-27T09:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T13:54:51.000Z","uid":36238,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcfa9a2618629980e9ed9a7f911c543332947faf","tid":376833,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/173249_90be0aeb0423d30731dc90d542330550.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F173249_90be0aeb0423d30731dc90d542330550.jpg&h=d714a0da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比來勢洶洶的「天鴿」，強烈熱帶風暴「帕卡」吹襲澳門時，風勢感覺溫和得多。澳門氣象局凌晨6時懸掛八號風球，起初雨勢猛烈，風力較強。至早上7時許，雨勢和風勢都明顯減弱，街上不時見到途人的蹤跡，有路人穿上用垃圾袋改製的雨衣，遮風擋雨，快捷又方便。<br />\n<br />\n有商舖無懼八號風球，照舊開舖。在澳門市政廳附近的輝記生果檔，六旬輝記夫婦於風雨中開舖。他們住在閣樓，逾40年來日日都開舖，「好話唔好聽，自己找食之餘，都可以方便街坊。」<br />\n<br />\n台灣旅客無懼八號波遊走大三巴<br />\n<br />\n風雨來襲卻無阻旅客觀光。在大三巴一帶，禮品店均未有開門營業，但附近仍有十幾名遊客觀光。<br />\n<br />\n來自台灣的李先生和李太太未有理會酒店職員的勸喻，走到大三巴一帶觀光。李太太笑言，相比台灣，「澳門這個is nothing ! 」她認為澳門在颱風期間，物價騰飛，「連一碗豆漿都要二十元」。<strong>二人認為天氣尚可接受</strong>，稍後時間會回到賭場試運氣。"},{"pid":"a937a905d355052e4ba1533e428916893866f314","tid":376833,"uid":36238,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:34:44.000Z","msg":"台灣人笑我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  台獨狗"},{"pid":"a86506c212af491e207181960b0bcc1b870a83fb","tid":376833,"uid":53811,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"佢地防風又真係勁ge"},{"pid":"2c9dae5591aedaa9d5dd61e19fc731a00800936c","tid":376833,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地防風又真係勁ge</blockquote><br />\n普通市民面對山泥傾瀉除咗走仲可以點"},{"pid":"08e4b19bb0d2d2c346eb1e4fd8df2158b01a9b46","tid":376833,"uid":84228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:44:38.000Z","msg":"澳門狗又唔屌柒台狗？"},{"pid":"b1d47535f8dae7e8d5c825db3413a03cd62c967e","tid":376833,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"050834ac428428b5a0620248711608cb8aa2913c","tid":376833,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:39:09.000Z","msg":"台灣成日打大風落大雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a815586837b5b24c190d119eb69d6ce5bf0a1bc2","tid":376833,"uid":65400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"澳門打風打到NOTHING<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf253b0afa38f606ad5ada5a557c5c7c83f0f4a","tid":376833,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"澳門這個is nothing 係指澳門係一無所有"},{"pid":"54053a828456d1efa24a8e239baea57696d9813a","tid":376833,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳門打風打到NOTHING<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}